Renée Lippin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9e_Lippin 0 Renée Lippin (born July 26, 1946) is a retired American actress. She appeared periodically on The Bob Newhart Show as Michelle Nardo, one of Dr. Hartley's patients on the television series. Lippin also guest starred on several other television series as well as appearing in feature films in the 1970s to 1990s. She and her husband, Dr. Allan Leicht have three children.
